Text: Yet another transparent ploy to scare people into buying crap. I'm sure that this "JohnDonym" keeps extensive logs of everything. heck, it's not even distributed, so one cop with a search warrant and the whole thing is gone. none of these "JohnDo" servers have an advertised latency UNDER 750ms. ... and they have ridiculously low speeds... 800kbit, heh. Why do you trust an unknown third party with your data if it's that same data you want to hide? :P
